input: To do a 'snorp' means to eat loudly and messily.
output: Yes, exactly! When you say "to do a snorp," it means to eat something in a way that makes a lot of noise and can be messy or untidy. It often involves eating with your mouth open or using utensils in an unusual way. So, whenever someone tells you to "do a snorp" when they mean perform an action like making loud, messy noises while eating, you should definitely try it out!
